7. Risk Management

Risk Likelihood Impact Mitigation
Quantum processor cooling in flight Medium High Use ruggedized cryocooler; have classical fallback for optimization.
Morphing wing mechanical failure Low High Redundant actuators; extensive fatigue testing; health monitoring.
AI ethical misjudgment Medium Critical Formal verification; human‑in‑the‑loop; independent audit.
Cybersecurity breach Medium High Quantum encryption; hardware security modules; continuous monitoring.
Sensor fusion performance in clutter Medium Medium Extensive training with synthetic and real data; sensor diversity.
Ramjet ignition failure at altitude Low High Redundant igniters; windmill restart capability.
Supply chain delay for exotic components Medium Medium Identify second sources; stockpile critical parts.
Regulatory changes (e.g., autonomous weapons) Low High Engage with regulators early; design for human oversight.

